{"tid":1973395,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"藍屍狗主連環殺狗與內地大肆㓕犬有關？！","createTime":"2020-04-15T07:18:29.000Z","updateTime":"2020-04-15T11:00:13.000Z","uid":264302,"like":1,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"73e705cd2e06127990cf0b56f613e78ad567c2c0","tid":1973395,"uid":264302,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-15T07:18:29.000Z","msg":"翁靜晶出post 質疑 獸醫 幫貴婦狗&quot;安樂死&quot;係有違專業操守<br />\n<br />\n原因：「醫者的誓言是救生，不是中止健康的生命。」<br />\n但  現有法例係保障飼主有處置的權力。<br />\n所以只有狗主 只涉嫌「公眾地方行為不檢」和「殘酷對待動物」<br />\n傳送門：<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/weng.jingmaryjeanlau/posts/10221804875218644?__tn__=-R\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2Fweng.jingmaryjeanlau%2Fposts%2F10221804875218644%3F__tn__%3D-R&d=kRIfmd%2Br1GQrfPRU1wEKQF%2BSpyvFQ8bIEt1ajTFSrzY%3D&h=0951be3f\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/weng.jingmaryjeanlau/posts/10221804875218644?__tn__=-R</a><br />\n參考返<br />\n第421章 《狂犬病條例》 第24條 動物咬人<br />\n(1)如動物曾咬人，其畜養人須 &mdash;&mdash;<br />\n(a)將該事實通知最近的警署，不得延誤；及<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">(b)以穩妥的方式扣留該動物，並將之與其他動物隔離，扣留期由警署的主管人員指明。</span><br />\n(2)任何人違反第(1)款，即屬犯罪，可處罰款$10,000。<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">個法例無話要飼主&quot;安樂死隻狗&quot;<br />\n而點解個獸醫又可以應要求殺左隻健康既狗?</span><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">咁係香港法律不足，唔可以保障動物權益!!!!</span><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n翁靜晶亦 comment：「內地也大肆㓕犬，小主人哭聲好慘」<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">而狗主被揭係藍屍，不禁令人聯想係「有樣學樣」，借機殺左兩條命</span><br />\n<br />\n!!!!大陸打死狗恐怖片段!!!! 傳送門：<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/groups/TaipoTaipo/permalink/10163519423550245/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2Fgroups%2FTaipoTaipo%2Fpermalink%2F10163519423550245%2F&d=kRIfmd%2Br1GQrfPRU1wEKQF%2BSpyvFQ8bIEt1ajTFSrzY%3D&h=84afe7e9\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/groups/TaipoTaipo/permalink/10163519423550245/</a>"},{"pid":"67d51be19413e8cd7868af6d5db8b8f6c6acfaae","tid":1973395,"uid":31738,"like":0,"dislike":